      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/12/happy-merry/#comment-18713"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-01-13T04:45:52-05:00">Wednesday, January 13, 2010 at 4:45 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Reading this post reminds me &#8212; I want to buy your book!  I am just about finished with Bob Spitz&#39; &#8220;The Saucier&#39;s Apprentice,&#8221; and need another book to get started on immediately following. <br />Of course, I&#39;ve wanted to get your book since I first read about it months ago, but it wasn&#39;t til reading your latest post that I was reminded of that fact &#8212; and just in the nick of time, too, when I am just about out of savory foodie reading!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-18713' data-commentid="18713" data-postid="908" data-belowelement="comment-18713" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Kimberly" aria-label='Reply to Kimberly'>Reply</a>    </div>
