      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/12/happy-merry/#comment-18714"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-01-13T16:22:14-05:00">Wednesday, January 13, 2010 at 4:22 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Turning over a new leaf, eh?  Like the new header!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-18714' data-commentid="18714" data-postid="908" data-belowelement="comment-18714" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to molly" aria-label='Reply to molly'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-18715" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/12/happy-merry/#comment-18715"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-01-18T23:00:45-05:00">Monday, January 18, 2010 at 11:00 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#39;m so sorry to contact you this way, but, I&#39;ve been reading your blog for two years now, and actually have occasion to visit Seattle for a few days, and would LOVE to come to Delancy for dinner.  Ordinarily, this would not be an issue, but, I come with an allergy to tomatoes&#8230;  I&#39;ve read in your sample menu, that you have some alternatives, yet, as it is a sample menu, and I&#39;d like to make reservations, shall I just call and see?  I didn&#39;t want to trouble anyone at a busy time, so thought that this could be the best way to go about it&#8230;  sorry if it&#39;s an inconvenience.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-18715' data-commentid="18715" data-postid="908" data-belowelement="comment-18715" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anonymous" aria-label='Reply to Anonymous'>Reply</a>    </div>
