      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/12/happy-merry/#comment-18717"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2010-01-19T18:10:48-05:00">Tuesday, January 19, 2010 at 6:10 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Anonymous, re: tomato allergies, no problem!  None of our current starters &#8211; we have four or five &#8211; has tomatoes right now, and we can easily do a pizza for you with no tomato sauce.  Not to worry!  We&#39;d love to have you.</p>
